{"tid":1453821,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港經濟戰再發一炮：轉數快+買實金","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T04:07:26.000Z","uid":99566,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"092b7cb52d541feb0a2413d81f1b59b660616b9e","tid":1453821,"uid":99566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"店主真係好憤怒，其實一直都留定一個行動，就係睇政府痛定思痛，回應訴求，結果琴晚發生繼612、721後另一慘案。我唔能夠有招唔教，今日就同大家講點樣買金幣，亦可以達至從銀行體系結餘同貨幣供應流走抽資的效果。<br />\n<br />\n首先有4種金幣有國際統一黃金成份規格、可以係世界流通及到外地銀行換當地貨幣，風險低、帶走方便。呢4種金幣分別係楓葉金幣(加拿大)、鷹揚金幣(美國)、鴻運金幣(澳洲)、熊貓金幣(中國)。<br />\n<br />\n我苦心同各位同業、大中小企、市民求助，本文最尾就係有提供實金買賣既銀行及官網，請去銀行總行買金幣，未有戶口就同場開戶，立即準備轉數快，一開就轉錢入新戶口扣錢買金幣。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家唔想搭車去總行，請到全港各銀行直接提取現金，擺係個嘉頓什錦餅乾鐵罐存起，將來一樣有機會用，一出糧就攞現金，大家好耐無對住實體鈔票，呢幾年只係望住數字，大家應該要攞出來數下銀紙。<br />\n<br />\n呢度店主補充大家努下，金管局係6月既既數字令大家鼓舞：<br />\n香港流通貨幣現金，係6月上升93億；當中港元現金係6月上升29億；<br />\n另外港元活期存款減少161億，大家係8月請繼續努力！<br />\n金管局數字：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/media/chi/doc/key-information/press-release/2019/20190731c8a1.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fmedia%2Fchi%2Fdoc%2Fkey-information%2Fpress-release%2F2019%2F20190731c8a1.pdf&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=7952dff8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/media/chi/doc/key-information/press-release/2019/20190731c8a1.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n永亨：楓葉金幣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ocbcwhhk.com/whb/action/rate/whbRate.do?id=fc_exchange_rate_gold&amp;locale=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ocbcwhhk.com%2Fwhb%2Faction%2Frate%2FwhbRate.do%3Fid%3Dfc_exchange_rate_gold%26locale%3Dzh-hk&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=51886f0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ocbcwhhk.com/whb/action/rate/whbRate.do?id=fc_exchange_rate_gold&amp;locale=zh-hk</a><br />\n中銀：楓葉金幣、熊貓金幣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bochk.com/tc/investment/rates/metal.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bochk.com%2Ftc%2Finvestment%2Frates%2Fmetal.html&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=a617dad9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bochk.com/tc/investment/rates/metal.html</a><br />\n招商永隆銀行：楓葉金幣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cmbwinglungbank.com/wlb_corporate/hk/personal/investments/gold-bar-and-gold-coin.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmbwinglungbank.com%2Fwlb_corporate%2Fhk%2Fpersonal%2Finvestments%2Fgold-bar-and-gold-coin.html&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=0db79ffc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cmbwinglungbank.com/wlb_corporate/hk/personal/investments/gold-bar-and-gold-coin.html</a><br />\n恆生：鴻運金幣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hangseng.com/zh-hk/rates/gold-prices/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hangseng.com%2Fzh-hk%2Frates%2Fgold-prices%2F&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=cee235a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hangseng.com/zh-hk/rates/gold-prices/</a><br />\n創興：楓葉金幣<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chbank.com/tc/financial/rates/gold-coin/index.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chbank.com%2Ftc%2Ffinancial%2Frates%2Fgold-coin%2Findex.shtml&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=d68ae421\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chbank.com/tc/financial/rates/gold-coin/index.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，大家要揸緊宗旨<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XgKazvhNYz8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXgKazvhNYz8&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=a5299626\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XgKazvhNYz8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/68380552_2429477070657381_5380035283767001088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_oc=AQmIZnlOtLTGROtYSHV085brvjlQizvyDQgfW1WZzlWnw9wneVY6Kk1BFvHUgbZw1PA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=01ef8b3aec7e098986d7214fbe318293&amp;oe=5DD2E895\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F68380552_2429477070657381_5380035283767001088_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_oc%3DAQmIZnlOtLTGROtYSHV085brvjlQizvyDQgfW1WZzlWnw9wneVY6Kk1BFvHUgbZw1PA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D01ef8b3aec7e098986d7214fbe318293%26oe%3D5DD2E895&h=0a2ca058&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2c9859207bfd27c0f1c55a3c03de9a26a06e9ae","tid":1453821,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c495805b4eb82bbcf4f161284e17580583115514","tid":1453821,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:32:25.000Z","msg":"不要香港買"},{"pid":"8f74377f15a81472570f370056b3abced5b0851b","tid":1453821,"uid":4739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"點解要教人買大陸金幣"},{"pid":"5ccf046b2ea53914ff3d626d630aad6c965583bc","tid":1453821,"uid":99566,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"8f74377f15a81472570f370056b3abced5b0851b","tid":1453821,"uid":4739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"點解要教人買大陸金幣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:45:50.000Z","msg":"我駁唔到，不過大陸金幣事實都有認受性，但能夠買就買左其他先<br />\n我個粒都買澳洲鴻運啦"},{"pid":"92056c1d658b7ec1ba86553d6158c995d608ebc3","tid":1453821,"uid":4739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5ccf046b2ea53914ff3d626d630aad6c965583bc","tid":1453821,"uid":99566,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"8f74377f15a81472570f370056b3abced5b0851b","tid":1453821,"uid":4739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"點解要教人買大陸金幣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:45:50.000Z","msg":"我駁唔到，不過大陸金幣事實都有認受性，但能夠買就買左其他先<br />\n我個粒都買澳洲鴻運啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"岩呀，我得另外三款金幣<br />\n等間買到假金未仆街，同埋一蚊不讓支那賺"},{"pid":"5fac2a04636f9cddc8a456959b49bb896cd593be","tid":1453821,"uid":78304,"like":14,"dislike